b'Hokuto no Ken: Raoh Gaiden Ten no Haoh: b'In the wastelands following the great nuclear war, a legend grew of a man.  \xe2\x80\x9cHokuto No Ken.\xe2\x80\x9d  The Fist of the North Star.
